\c 17
\s Tsvimbo yaAroni
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha akataura naMosesi, akati,
\v 2 "Taura navana vaIsiraeri, utore kwavari tsvintho, irrkwe mba imwe neimwe yamadzibaba avo, tsvimbo dzine gumi nembiri, pamachinda avo ose nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo; zvino unofanira kunyora zita romumwe nomumwe patsvimbo yake.
\v 3 Asi zita
\p raAroni unofanira kurinyora patsvimbo yaRevhi; nokuti kunofanira kuva netsvimbo imwe yomukuru mumwe nomumwe wedzimba dzamadzibaba avo.
\v 4 Zvino unofanira kudzichengeta mutende rokusangana pamberi peareka yechipupuriro, pandinosangana nemi.
\v 5 Ipapo munhu andichatsaura, tsvimbo yake ichabuka, kuti ndigumise kunyunyuta kwavana vaIsiraeri kwavanokunyunyutira nako."
\v 6 Zvino Mosesi akataura navana vaIsiraeri, machinda avo ose akamupa tsvimbo, imwe yomuchinda mumwe nomumwe nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, ndidzo tsvimbo gumi nembiri; netsvimbo yaAroni yakanga iri pakati petsvimbo dzavo.
\v 7 Mosesi akachengeta tsvimbo idzo pamberi paJehovha mutende rechipupuriro.
\v 8 Fume mangwana Mosesi akapinda mutende rechipupuriro, onei tsvimbo yaAroni yeimba yaRevhi yakanga yabuka, yava namabukira, yabudisa maruva, yabereka maamanda akanga aibva.
\v 9 Ipapo Mosesi akabudisa tsvimbo dzose pamberi paJehovha kuvanhu vaIsiraeri vose; vakatarira, mumwe nomumwe akatora tsvimbo yake.
\v 10 Jehovha akati kuna Mosesi, "Dzosera tsvimbo yaAroni pamberi pechipupuriro, ichengetwe chive chiratidzo chavanhu vakandimukira; kuti ugumise kundinyunyutira kwavo, varege kufa."
\v 11 Mosesi akaita saizvozvo; sezvaakarairwa naJehovha, ndizvo zvaakaita.
\p
\v 12 Vana vaIsiraeri vakataura naMosesi, vakati, "Tarira, tofa, topera, topera tose.
\v 13 Mumwe nomumwe anoswedera, anoswedera kutabhenakeri yaJehovha, anofa; zvino tichafa tose kanhi?"

